00:15:18.751 --> 00:15:20.920 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
[Kotetsu] <i>Ah, those things are</i>
<i>too stuffy for me.</i>

277
00:15:21.087 --> 00:15:23.256 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
There's tons of free food
and all the suits are here.

278
00:15:24.340 --> 00:15:26.175 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[Kotetsu] <i>Say hi for me, will ya?</i>

279
00:15:26.968 --> 00:15:28.469 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[Rock Bison] Hello? Hello!?

280
00:15:29.971 --> 00:15:30.972 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[squealing]

281
00:15:31.055 --> 00:15:33.307 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Hmm! Bison's got some
junk in the trunk!

282
00:15:33.516 --> 00:15:35.893 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
[Rock Bison] Stop! Stop!
Get offa me!

283
00:15:36.144 --> 00:15:38.646 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
You got your screen-time
out there as usual.

284
00:15:38.729 --> 00:15:40.523 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Keep it up, it's great exposure.

285
00:15:40.606 --> 00:15:42.400 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
[Origami] I won't let
the sponsors down, sir!

286
00:15:42.942 --> 00:15:44.402 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I mean, I hope not...

287
00:15:45.403 --> 00:15:46.404 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
You're not listening.

288
00:15:46.529 --> 00:15:49.740 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
My catchphrase is stupid, can't
your company let me change it?

289
00:15:49.866 --> 00:15:53.327 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
That domineering attitude of yours
is why people love you.

290
00:15:53.411 --> 00:15:54.829 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[chuckles] Why change what works?

291
00:15:55.121 --> 00:15:58.332 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
It's all about the fans!
Thanks, and thanks again!

292
00:15:58.458 --> 00:15:59.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Hello, Mr. Maverick!

293
00:16:00.334 --> 00:16:04.797 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Ah! I knew promoting you to producer
was the right choice for Hero TV.

294
00:16:05.465 --> 00:16:07.842 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
But I never expected you
to pull in these ratings.

295
00:16:08.134 --> 00:16:10.803 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Well when it comes to
creating a spectacle...

296
00:16:11.637 --> 00:16:13.264 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I stop at nothing.

297
00:16:13.931 --> 00:16:15.099 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[phone ringing]

298
00:16:15.224 --> 00:16:16.767 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[Kotetsu] <i>Yeah, yeah, coming.</i>

299
00:16:17.310 --> 00:16:18.686 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[groaning]

300
00:16:20.855 --> 00:16:22.190 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Yello?
-[Kaede] <i>Dad?</i>

301
00:16:22.440 --> 00:16:25.026 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Honey! What's goin' on, Kaede?

302
00:16:25.401 --> 00:16:28.779 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Tomorrow's my recital...
You didn't forget, did you?

303
00:16:28.946 --> 00:16:32.658 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Forget? I said I'd be there
and I will! Ow!

304
00:16:32.950 --> 00:16:34.243 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
You mean it?

305
00:16:34.327 --> 00:16:36.621 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
You're not gonna have to work
like you usually do?!

306
00:16:36.704 --> 00:16:37.747 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[Kotetsu] <i>No way.</i>

307
00:16:37.872 --> 00:16:40.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Tomorrow you are gonna be the
cutest little girl on stage

308
00:16:40.500 --> 00:16:43.044 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
and I'm gonna be the first in line
to see you perform!

309
00:16:43.211 --> 00:16:44.921 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
I wouldn't miss it
for the world!

310
00:16:45.004 --> 00:16:46.464 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
[Anju]
<i>You said that last time.</i>

311
00:16:46.547 --> 00:16:47.757 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[grimaces]

312
00:16:48.007 --> 00:16:49.383 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Uh! You know, you should
say something

313
00:16:49.467 --> 00:16:51.052 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
when you take the phone, mom!

314
00:16:51.135 --> 00:16:53.679 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
I saw you on TV. Do you
have to pay for all that?

315
00:16:53.763 --> 00:16:55.264 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[Kotetsu chuckling] <i>Real funny, mom.</i>

316
00:16:55.389 --> 00:16:59.101 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
All I'm saying is that you should
really try to be more careful, dear.

317
00:16:59.352 --> 00:17:00.561 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Yeah, I know.

318
00:17:00.686 --> 00:17:03.814 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
[Anju] <i>I mean it. If something horrible</i>
<i>were to happen to you,</i>

319
00:17:03.898 --> 00:17:08.444 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>I'd have to tell little Kaede about</i>
<i>your work as a superhero at your funeral.</i>

320
00:17:08.611 --> 00:17:10.196 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>She'd be so heartbroken.</i>

321
00:17:10.279 --> 00:17:11.864 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
You always worry too much.

322
00:17:11.948 --> 00:17:13.491 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[Anju] <i>Well can you blame me?</i>

323
00:17:13.658 --> 00:17:16.911 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>A man who's away from his family and</i>
<i>faces criminals everyday</i>

324
00:17:16.994 --> 00:17:18.204 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>just to make a living...</i>

325
00:17:18.329 --> 00:17:19.497 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Of course, I worry!</i>

326
00:17:19.580 --> 00:17:23.417 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
[Kotetsu] Yeah, I know.
Believe me. I know.

327
00:17:30.132 --> 00:17:31.133 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Huh!?

328
00:17:31.342 --> 00:17:34.720 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-I'm sorry, Kotetsu.
-[gasps] Ben?

329
00:17:35.805 --> 00:17:36.806 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[Kotetsu] A buyout?

330
00:17:36.889 --> 00:17:38.391 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[Ben] It was the only option.

331
00:17:38.724 --> 00:17:40.268 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Ad revenue kept falling

332
00:17:40.518 --> 00:17:43.312 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
and we were lucky to find a buyer
willing to take on our debts.

333
00:17:44.063 --> 00:17:45.064 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Here.

334
00:17:45.189 --> 00:17:47.483 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Huh? Who's this Lloyds guy?

335
00:17:47.608 --> 00:17:49.026 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Your new employer.

336
00:17:49.402 --> 00:17:50.403 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Huh?

337
00:17:50.528 --> 00:17:52.697 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
And I would suggest you
go and pay him a visit.

338
00:17:52.989 --> 00:17:56.075 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
What?! Hang on a second,
what the hell is goin' on?!

339
00:17:56.242 --> 00:17:57.493 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Starting this next season,

340
00:17:57.577 --> 00:18:00.955 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
only the seven biggest corporations
are going to be sponsoring heroes.

341
00:18:01.789 --> 00:18:04.542 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Hate to say it, but our company
just dropped off the list.

342
00:18:04.709 --> 00:18:07.044 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
So, you're just gonna disappear,
just like that?

343
00:18:07.253 --> 00:18:09.171 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Hey, business is
business.

344
00:18:09.463 --> 00:18:11.674 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Do all the other heroes
know about this?

345
00:18:14.510 --> 00:18:16.220 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I'm last to know.

346
00:18:16.429 --> 00:18:17.555 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[Ben] Sorry old pal.

347
00:18:18.639 --> 00:18:19.890 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[Kotetsu] What'll happen to you?

348
00:18:20.057 --> 00:18:21.642 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[Ben] Oh, don't worry about me.

349
00:18:21.726 --> 00:18:25.813 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
I'm gonna relax, collect my unemployment
and look for work in a few months.

350
00:18:26.230 --> 00:18:28.316 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
So, I'll be alone at
this new place?

351
00:18:28.566 --> 00:18:30.484 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-You'll be fine.
-But Ben--

352
00:18:31.569 --> 00:18:32.903 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Times are changing.

353
00:18:34.071 --> 00:18:37.366 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
I'm really gonna miss being
in your corner and watching you fight.

354
00:18:37.617 --> 00:18:38.868 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Really.

355
00:18:39.201 --> 00:18:40.870 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
But no matter what happens,

356
00:18:41.162 --> 00:18:43.456 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I'll always be Wild Tiger's biggest fan.

357
00:18:54.884 --> 00:18:55.885 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Hmm?

358
00:18:56.886 --> 00:18:58.220 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[chuckling]

359
00:19:00.514 --> 00:19:01.682 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Ahhh!

360
00:19:01.766 --> 00:19:03.392 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[humming]

361
00:19:04.185 --> 00:19:05.895 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
This is the place.

362
00:19:06.687 --> 00:19:07.938 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Huh?

363
00:19:11.067 --> 00:19:12.276 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Hmm...

364
00:19:15.154 --> 00:19:16.697 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[grunts] I got it!

365
00:19:20.910 --> 00:19:22.578 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[grunts] Here ya go.

366
00:19:22.745 --> 00:19:23.913 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Ah, thank you.

367
00:19:24.330 --> 00:19:26.540 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Um, I think you dropped
your cards.

368
00:19:26.957 --> 00:19:28.918 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Ah! Oh, those are just--

369
00:19:29.251 --> 00:19:31.504 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
It's okay, mister.
I understand.

370
00:19:32.004 --> 00:19:34.674 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
[laughs] Darn, ya figured it
out, huh kid?

371
00:19:34.757 --> 00:19:37.343 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
You like Wild Tiger,
'cause he's old, like you!

372
00:19:37.551 --> 00:19:40.554 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
[laughing]
Say what now?

373
00:19:41.013 --> 00:19:42.848 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Here, you can
have this one!

374
00:19:42.932 --> 00:19:45.726 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
You should keep that,
I'm sure it means a lot to you.

375
00:19:45.810 --> 00:19:48.896 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Actually, I'm a Sky High fan,
so I don't need. it. Take it!

376
00:19:49.105 --> 00:19:51.190 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Uh, thanks.

377
00:19:53.275 --> 00:19:56.028 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[sighs] That's how it is.

378
00:20:01.325 --> 00:20:03.077 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
So, you're Wild Tiger.

379
00:20:03.869 --> 00:20:06.997 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
And I see your real name here,
but how do I pronounce it?

380
00:20:07.164 --> 00:20:09.375 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
It's Kotetsu. Kotetsu
Kaburagi.

381
00:20:10.084 --> 00:20:11.252 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[Alexander Lloyds] Hmmm...

382
00:20:12.628 --> 00:20:16.298 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Right. You'll be briefed on your new suit
in the Design Department.

383
00:20:16.757 --> 00:20:19.510 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Oh, I hadn't planned
on starting today.

384
00:20:19.760 --> 00:20:21.929 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Or you can just quit if
you don't like it.

385
00:20:22.263 --> 00:20:23.431 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Today works.

386
00:20:23.556 --> 00:20:25.349 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[alarm sounding]

387
00:20:25.641 --> 00:20:27.351 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[Lloyds] The industrial district.

388
00:20:29.520 --> 00:20:30.980 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
The Steel Hammer Statue?

389
00:20:31.397 --> 00:20:32.732 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Why is it moving?

390
00:20:33.023 --> 00:20:34.859 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
I bet a NEXT is behind
this.

391
00:20:34.984 --> 00:20:36.736 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
All right, you'd better
get going.

392
00:20:36.986 --> 00:20:39.572 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Huh? Oh, but I don't
have my suit with me.

393
00:20:39.697 --> 00:20:41.866 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
No need. I have your new
one right here.

394
00:20:42.158 --> 00:20:43.159 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Uhhh...

395
00:20:44.285 --> 00:20:47.079 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
This is a perfect chance
to debut your new look.

396
00:20:48.497 --> 00:20:50.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
I don't think I
can do that... sir.

397
00:20:51.459 --> 00:20:53.169 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Really? And why
is that?

398
00:20:53.377 --> 00:20:56.505 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
It's just--- I've worn the same suit
my entire career.

399
00:20:56.589 --> 00:20:57.715 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[Lloyds] <i>Don't be nervous,</i>

400
00:20:57.798 --> 00:21:00.968 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>the tech on this suit is far better</i>
<i>than that old one you're used to.</i>

401
00:21:01.469 --> 00:21:03.679 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
[Kotetsu] <i>Yeah, that's not the</i>
<i>issue here.</i>

402
00:21:03.929 --> 00:21:05.723 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
That costume defines my life.

403
00:21:05.931 --> 00:21:07.683 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
It's everything I am as a hero.

404
00:21:08.100 --> 00:21:10.644 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>A symbol of hope and justice!</i>

405
00:21:10.728 --> 00:21:12.688 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Just wear the thing or you're fired.

406
00:21:12.855 --> 00:21:14.356 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[emergency vehicle sirens wailing]

407
00:21:30.456 --> 00:21:32.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Actually, this thing is
really cool.

408
00:21:34.543 --> 00:21:36.921 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
There you are.
Let's do this.

409
00:21:37.046 --> 00:21:38.881 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[Lloyds] <i>There is one other thing...</i>

410
00:21:39.131 --> 00:21:41.425 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
We've decided to partner you up
with another hero.

411
00:21:41.509 --> 00:21:42.510 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Huh?

412
00:21:42.593 --> 00:21:44.428 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Apollon Media is going to sell it as the

413
00:21:44.512 --> 00:21:47.223 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
first-ever Superhero Duo
to take the stage.

414
00:21:47.306 --> 00:21:49.225 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Nobody asked me
about that.

415
00:21:49.308 --> 00:21:51.769 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
That's because you don't
have a say in the matter.

416
00:21:55.022 --> 00:21:56.732 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Where's my teammate, anyway?

417
00:21:56.816 --> 00:21:58.234 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
And who the hell are they giving me?

418
00:21:58.317 --> 00:22:00.027 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[screaming]

419
00:22:01.779 --> 00:22:04.782 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Damn that hurt. Guess I can't
take this guy alone.

420
00:22:05.407 --> 00:22:06.992 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
What? It's you?!

